newsitem.title: UK: LIFFE Dec white sugar deliveries total 235 lots.
newsitem.headline: LIFFE Dec white sugar deliveries total 235 lots.

text.p: A total of 235 lots of white sugar, equivalent to 11,750 tonnes, was delivered against the London December No.5 contract after it expired on Friday, the London International Financial Futures Exchange (LIFFE) said.
E D & F Man 80 Refco Gdynia
E D & F Man 2 Refco Eemshaven
